With his mother and grandfather .. Watch a rare video of Haitham Ahmed Zaki
07 Nov 2019, 11:07 by Art Department
Department of Art The circulation of a number of pioneers of social networking sites video rarely for the late artist Haitham Ahmed Zaki, a young child accompanied by his mother Hala Fouad and grandfather director Ahmed Fouad. This rare video is part of a television interview with the great media Salma Shamma while hosting her grandfather director Ahmed Fouad and his mother artist Hala Fouad. The child Haitham Ahmed Zaki appeared in this television meeting a lot of shame and little talk and did not want to pay attention to the camera a lot. It is noteworthy that in the early hours of Thursday morning, the young artist Haytham Ahmed Zaki died at the age of 35 years;
